   <title>
    【圖輯】華豐大廈大火．一個月
   </title>
   <link>
    https://www.inmediahk.net/node/%E6%94%BF%E7%B6%93/%E3%80%90%E5%9C%96%E8%BC%AF%E3%80%91%E8%8F%AF%E8%B1%90%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%88%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%AB%EF%BC%8E%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88
   </link>
   <description>
    <![CDATA[<div class="field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-18 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">內容: </div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/5030">政經</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-image field-type-image field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Ffiles%2Fcolumn_images%2F202405101.png" width="940" height="492" alt="" /></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-19 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">自由標籤: </div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/539137">華豐大廈</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/taxonomy/term/528473">獨媒報導</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p><font color="red">【獨媒報導】</font>華豐大火事發至今一個月，低層仍然滿目瘡痍。早前宣布結業的勁力健身中心 ，牆身及地板都被燒得燻黑，健身器具上沾滿煙灰及泥土。大廈四部升降機中只有一部運作正常，部分居民選擇行樓梯出入。後樓梯佈滿雜物，包括按摩椅及大量垃圾。</p>
<p>攝影：米</p>
<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/2q9LL3FH56" title="勁力健美中心"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53709321708_cc97fe002f_z.jpg" width="640" alt="勁力健美中心" /></a></p>
<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/2q9LL3FH56" title="勁力健美中心"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53709321708_cc97fe002f_z.jpg" width="640" alt="勁力健美中心" /></a></p>
<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/BVJ7NY4TaL" title="Untitled"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53709321718_14c589c65a_z.jpg" width="640" alt="Untitled" /></a></p>
<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/97597572Wt" title="Untitled"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53709321713_3caeac45ec_z.jpg" width="640" alt="Untitled" /></a></p>
<p>多間賓館的老闆都指火災後因停電以及電梯故障生意清零。有業主打算入屋取文件，惟到達門口才發現單位大門被警方上鎖。大廈偷竊案頻生，後樓梯張貼了小偷的照片。</p>
<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/v738899C3e" title="Untitled"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53708212652_4951361c45_z.jpg" width="640" alt="Untitled" /></a></p>
<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/aDt772cHo8" title="Untitled"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53709543195_7d3803de1b_z.jpg" width="640" alt="Untitled" /></a></p>
<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/06q8q0Gu2t" title="Untitled"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53709111666_f15cd1ceca_z.jpg" width="640" alt="Untitled" /></a></p>
